descriptionHtml:
Just another player house.

Includes:
200+ containers
25 mannequins
28 display cases
20 weapon plaques
Full blacksmith area
Enchanting table 
2 alchemy tables
4 prisoners (do what you want with them, they respawn.)
Custom Guards (complete with arrow in the knee dialogue.)

to find the shack type in coc dovahkiinoutside and look to the right and the shack should be there.

If you find any bugs let me know and i will try to fix them.
========================================================
Version 2 update.

Added map marker
Updated house
Brightened light in mannequin and display case room.
author: poptart11
